description: Daylight pours through big windows on all three exposures of this move-in ready end-unit town-home. Choose to enter through your private courtyard or through your private 2-car garage. The patio also features built in pet grass so you can easily let Fido out to do their business. A cozy mudroom and coat closet at ground level offer the perfect place to stash your coats and shoes before heading upstairs. The first floor offers an open layout with a spacious living room, oak hardwood floors, and expansive floor-to-ceiling windows flooding the space with light. It also features a cozy gas fireplace, a functional office nook, and built in surround sound speakers. On the second floor, discover two beautifully appointed bedrooms with spacious closets and a well-appointed shared bathroom with double sinks. The top floor includes a well appointed primary suite with en-suite bathroom and sliding doors leading to a private deck. Welcome home!
